1708
02:38:43,913 --> 02:38:46,491
You mustn't take it too much to heart though lad.

1709
02:38:46,677 --> 02:38:50,467
He loves to exagerate the worst in himself when he's drunk.

1710
02:38:50,468 --> 02:38:52,294
He's devoted to you.

1711
02:38:52,681 --> 02:38:55,285
