1767
02:45:01,347 --> 02:45:04,624
- I know it's something I lost.
- Mary.

1768
02:45:04,625 --> 02:45:06,688
No good Papa.

1769
02:45:06,689 --> 02:45:11,456
Something I... I miss...
terribly.

1770
02:45:12,107 --> 02:45:15,599
- It... it can't be all together lost.
- Mama.

1771
02:45:16,094 --> 02:45:18,182
- Something...
- What's the use...?

1772
02:45:18,183 --> 02:45:20,379
...I need terribly.

1773
02:45:21,321 --> 02:45:27,185
I remember, when I had it I was never lonely nor afraid.

1774
02:45:29,765 --> 02:45:32,513
I can't have lost it forever.

1775
02:45:33,120 --> 02:45:39,142
